Selfie Now! The best app for taking a quick Selfie and editing it immediately. With over 50+ edits you are sure to create a perfect Selfie!

Selfies are great. We all take them. It feels good. This apps makes it super easy to take selfie quickly.

Share your selfie with your friends on Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter. You can also email your Selfie or save it to your camera roll.

Yoodle.me app is the easiest way to contact and to exchange with your city. Without registration!

Yoodle.me is THE location-based app that brings together an entire city (or stadium or event or fair) in one public timeline and in one messenger group, incl. 1:1 messaging. 

Yoodle is about Right Here and Right Now. All Yoodle users are live reporters about the Here and Now in their city: make posts especially on #party #goingout #nightlife #clubbing #queues (in front of clubs) #crowd #style #streetart #shopping (windows) #food #activities and create a public common timeline for your event or your city. In order to let other locals also know (crowd wisdom) and to inspire them (crowd inspiration) and to easily connect with your city (crowd connector).

All Yoodle users/locals are in one public timeline. All users/locals can do 1:1 messaging without any hurdles. All without registration! In Yoodle you can see who is around you and Yoodle tells you what is happening around you. 

Yoodle is not about your friends, it is about the people near you (potential new friends), and the things that are happing around you. Therefore, Yoodle is not competing with Facebook, WhatsApp, Twitter and Instagram, but is a very good situative completion of these apps. 

Yoodle does not connect with your digital footprint in any way. In Yoodle you can be whoever you want to be in any situation.
In Yoodle, everyone is a live reporter. 

Some inspiration for what to do in Yoodle: 
• City reporting - let others know what’s going on
• Share your experience – show your best findings
• Find other people for spontaneous activities 
• Get creative with others
• Create some funny challenges

CVS Photo Printing with Genuine Kodak Moments paper! 
 
Send photos to print at any CVS location:
1 Select pictures from your phone 
2 Choose print sizes 
3 Order for printing at your nearest favorite CVS store 

High quality photo prints available for 1 hour pick up. 
 Make Lasting Memories with CVS Photo Prints: 
Use Photo Prints Now to print your best memories at CVS locations. Transform treasured moments into wall decorations using our large print sizes. Print photos and pick up in 1 hour at your nearest CVS store. Print Instagram, Facebook, Flickr, Dropbox & Print Google+ pictures. Easily access photos wherever you have them stored.  
Simply the Best CVS Photo Printing App: 
Faster than kiosks, and super simple to use. We use high quality Kodak paper to make a lasting archive of your life’s memories. Perfect for scrapbooking or a little extra love to make a greeting card extra special. Transform your memories into the perfect printed photo masterpieces.
 CVS Photo Print Sizes: • 4x6” Photo Prints • 5x7” Photo Prints • 8x10” Photo Prints
• 6x6” Square Instagram Prints • 8x8” Square Instagram Prints

After selecting your favorite memories for printing, use the change size and quantity screen to change print sizes and then, simply send them to CVS to print within the hour. No subscriptions or other gimmicks. Get your phone’s pictures into print quickly and easily.
